title: E-ON Magazine #010 DVD
description: E-ON Magazine is the official hard-copy magazine of EVE Online. Published quarterly, it contains a wealth of interviews, features, character and CCP staff profiles, ship reviews and set-up guidance, exclusive fiction and player guides, along with all the latest news from the world of EVE. The issue that accompanied this DVD (#010) contains an exclusive nine-page guide to your first days in New Eden. Back issues are still available. Full details are available at http://www.eve-online.com/eon
